        "x": 0,
        "y": 40,
        "width": 100,
        "height": 60
      }
    },
    {
      "type": "paragraph",
      "text": "GIVEN under my hand and seal of Said County Court at Office in Henderson, this 22nd day of August A. D. 1867",
